==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: wū lòu piān féng lián yè yŭ
===Etymology===
Literally: When the roof is leaking, that's when you'll get several continuous nights of rain.
===Proverb===
# [[When it rains, it pours]].

